### HYMN LXI

#### A prayer for sacred knowledge and its fruits

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0706101">1</span></span>Since, Agni,
with our fervent zeal we undergo austerity,  
  May we be dear to Sacred Lore, may we be wise and live long  
   lives.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0706102">2</span></span>Agni, we
practise acts austere, we undergo austerity.  
  So listening to Holy Lore may we grow wise and full of days.

